::FZ/Reptilica::

FZ nods. "Allright, then lets get back to the base first."

Three shuttles land to the side of him and the seven bots, the 
hatches opening. Each shuttle could hold three. FZ walks into one and 
Reptilica into another, motioning for the seven new Alliance members 
to follow.
